Title: Integrability and Seiberg-Witten theory

Authors: H. Itoyama and A. Morozov

Comments: 21 pages, talk given by A.M. in the conference `` Frontiers in

Quantum Field Theory'' in honor of Professor Keiji Kikkawa's 60th birthdayA summary of results is presented, which provide exact description of thelow-energy $4d$ $N=2$ and $N=4$ SUSY gauge theories in terms of $1d$ integrablesystems.